high_descs: Turn right, walk to the TV shelf
Grab the water can in the shelf
Turn left, and turn left, walk to the corner with a floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Grab the white water can in the tv shelf, turn on the floor lamp

high_descs: Move across the room to the red wooden TV stand
pick up the white tea pot on the bottom shelf of the TV stand
Carry the tea pot to the floor lamp to the right of the sofa
Turn on the lamp while holding the tea pot
anns.task_desc: Carry a tea pot while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn around and go to the TV stand.
Turn left, then left again to go to the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Look at the watering can using light from the lamp.
